<h2 style="border: 1px solid black; background: #CE1126; color: white; padding: .1em; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing:3px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 100%; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom: none; font-family: sans-serif;"><span class="mw-headline" id="Did_you_know_..."><i>Did you know ...</i></span></h2>
<div style="display: block; border: 1px solid black; vertical-align: top; background: white; color: black; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 1em; margin-top: 0em; padding-top: .3em;">
<p><span style="text-align: right; float:right; margin:-.9em -.9em .3em .3em; padding: -.9em -.9em .3em .3em;"><small class="editlink noprint plainlinksneverexpand"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Portal_Burundi_Did_you_know&action=edit.php.html">edit</a></small></span></p>
<ul>
<li style="-moz-float-edge: content-box">... that the recent <b><a href="Persecution_of_albinos" title="Persecution of albinos" class="mw-redirect">persecution of albinos</a></b> in <a href="Tanzania" title="Tanzania">Tanzania</a> and <a href="Burundi" title="Burundi">Burundi</a> is based on the <a href="Superstition" title="Superstition">belief</a> that their body parts have <a href="Witchcraft" title="Witchcraft">magical power</a> and impart <a href="Prosperity" title="Prosperity">prosperity</a>?
