<dd><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Flag_of_Burundi.svg" class="image"><img alt="Flag of Burundi.svg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/50/Flag_of_Burundi.svg/18px-Flag_of_Burundi.svg.png" width="18" height="11" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/50/Flag_of_Burundi.svg/27px-Flag_of_Burundi.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/50/Flag_of_Burundi.svg/36px-Flag_of_Burundi.svg.png 2x" /></a> <a href="Wikipedia_WikiProject_Burundi" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Burundi">WikiProject Burundi</a></dd>
